      "description": "Three mesh refinement levels (coarse: 2.1M cells, medium: 5.8M cells, fine: 14.3M cells) were evaluated. The Grid Convergence Index (GCI) for the volume-averaged scalar shear stress was 3.2% between the medium and fine meshes, meeting the MRL 2 requirement of GCI < 5%. The medium mesh was selected for production runs.",
